on is unavailable\"是TiDB特有的区域不可用错误\n- **错误传播**: 数据库错误通过ProductCatalogService传播到前端和结账服务\n\n### 4. **影响范围**\n- **直接影响**: Frontend、CheckoutService、RecommendationService都依赖ProductCatalogService\n- **间接影响**: 整个电商系统的产品查询、推荐、结账功能都受到影响\n\n**结论**: 故障的根本原因是TiDB数据库出现区域不可用问题，导致依赖它的ProductCatalogService无法正常工作，进而影响整个系统的产品相关功能。\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nNo consensus yet\n\n--- Metric Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Trace Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nAGREED", "log_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "metric_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "trace_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "report_analysis_findings": {"uuid": "91b14fe1-386", "component": "tidb-tikv", "reason": "Region is unavailable causing Error 9005 (HY000) and failed_query_ops spike from 0 to 42.67", "reasoning_trace": [{"step": 1, "action": "LoadMetrics(tidb-tikv)", "observation": "failed_query_ops increased from 0 to 42.67, duration_99th spiked from 0.01ms to 64.85ms"}, {"step": 2, "action": "LogSearch(productcatalogservice)", "observation": "Found Region is unavailable Error 9005 (HY000) in productcatalogservice logs 148 times"}, {"step": 3, "action": "TraceAnalysis(91b14fe1-386)", "observation": "productcatalogservice GetProduct calls show Error 9005 (HY000) Region is unavailable status"}]}, "report_analysis_completed": true}
